# Dandelion product identity.
#
# This file mirrors the key=value format of Chromium's own BRANDING files
# (chrome/app/theme/chromium/BRANDING). The `dandelion/branding` GN action
# consumes it so that product identity has exactly one source of truth, rather
# than being duplicated across the installer, updater, crash reporter and
# Windows version resources.
#
# Changing a value here changes it everywhere. Do not hardcode these strings
# anywhere else in the tree.

